The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Smriti scare

 Mumbai, March 16 (PTI) Television actor and BJP star campaigner Smriti Irani today said she had sought police protection after receiving threats.

 ?I have been receiving threats over telephone for the past two weeks,? she said.

 ?I realised I was being stalked. The caller had minute details of my movements.... Police are investigating the case and I hope they would be able to trace the people behind these threats,? Irani said.




